{"about_the_game":"Your purpose in this game is finding evidences and taking videos of paranormal activities to share on your website named \u2018Psychoscopy\u2019. You have different types of equipments to detect specific activities for finding haunted areas and gather evidences of these existences. Your exploration team checks the place before you reach the destination and gives you some information about it. You earn your life with sharing the videos and the evidences of paranormal activities on your website.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">   <li>In Psychoscopy, there are 20+ unique existences in 4 different categories. <br>   </li><li>These are; ghosts, spirits, daemons and mytical beings. <br>   </li><li>All of them have unique defense methods that helps you to defend yourselves while looking for an evidence.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1481210/extras/Store_Menu_2.png?t=1730144041\" /><br><br>You can contribute to the development of the game by coming to our Steam community or our Discord channel and sharing your suggestions or opinions with us.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">PROTECT YOURSELF</h2><br>You will find yourselves in the middle of the different existences. You have to know which creature you are dealing before chosing the defense method. While these methods helps you to defend yourselves against some creatures, they can make others angry.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">TALK TO THEM</h2><br>Some of the beings may want to talk with you, you can contact with them, ask them questions, tell them to do some activities or maybe talk with them by using an ouija board.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">LARGE MAPS</h2><br>The places you will search have large lands. There are many places worth to visit, but it can be hard to find your way. You should read your exploration team\u2019s hints carefully and check the map frequently that is given to you by them. You and your 4 friends should choose where you check wisely beca